    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a masterclass in JDM engineering: a 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo preserved in exceptional mechanical state. This A80 chassis retains its original 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six, exhibiting factory-spec compression and zero evidence of oil blow-by or thermal degradation. The sequential CT20 turbochargers provide a linear torque curve, managed by the original Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox which features crisp synchronization and precise gate engagement. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showcasing untouched double-wishbone suspension components and original VIN tags on all body panels. Power is delivered through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and cornering stability. This is a mechanically pure, investment-grade example for the collector who values engineering provenance and performance ceiling.",
      "price": 49500.0,
